'''硒化亚锡'''，又称'''一硒化锡'''，是一种无机化合物，化学式为SnSe。它是窄带隙(IV-VI)[[半导体|半导体]]，人们对其在低成本[[光伏器件|光伏器件]]和存储器开关器件的应用有着相当大的兴趣。<ref>[http://www.sigmaaldrich.com/catalog/product/aldrich/751448?lang=en&region=US Tin(II) selenide] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sigmaaldrich.com/catalog/product/aldrich/751448?lang=en&region=US |date=20170401231220 }}. sigmaaldrich.com</ref>硒化亚锡是典型的层状金属[[硫属化物|硫属化物]]，<ref name=r1>{{cite journal|doi=10.1021/nn5004315|pmid=24601530|title=Two-Dimensional Tin Selenide Nanostructures for Flexible All-Solid-State Supercapacitors|journal=ACS Nano|volume=8|issue=4|pages=3761–70|year=2014|last1=Zhang|first1=Chunli|last2=Yin|first2=Huanhuan|last3=Han|first3=Min|last4=Dai|first4=Zhihui|last5=Pang|first5=Huan|last6=Zheng|first6=Yulin|last7=Lan|first7=Ya-Qian|last8=Bao|first8=Jianchun|last9=Zhu|first9=Jianmin}}</ref>即[[氧族元素|第16族]]阴离子（Se<sup>2-</sup>）和正电性元素阳离子（Sn<sup>2+</sup>）以层状结构排列。

硒化亚锡有着低导热性和合适的导电性，为用于热电材料提供了可能性。<ref>Northwestern University. [http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2014/04/140417124519.htm "Surprising material could play huge role in saving energy: Tin selenide is best at converting waste heat to electricity."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2014/04/140417124519.htm |date=20180117191119 }} ScienceDaily, 17 April 2014.</ref>在2014年，[[西北大学_(伊利诺伊州)|西北大学]]的一个团队在热电材料效率方面创造了世界纪录。<ref>{{cite journal|pmid=24740068|year=2014|author1=Zhao|first1=L. D.|title=Ultralow thermal conductivity and high thermoelectric figure of merit in Sn ''Se'' crystals|journal=Nature|volume=508|issue=7496|pages=373–7|last2=Lo|first2=S. H.|last3=Zhang|first3=Y|last4=Sun|first4=H|last5=Tan|first5=G|last6=Uher|first6=C|last7=Wolverton|first7=C|last8=Dravid|first8=V. P.|last9=Kanatzidis|first9=M. G.|doi=10.1038/nature13184}}</ref>

